query:
SELECT c1.time
                FROM ohlc_candles c1
                INNER JOIN LATERAL (
                    SELECT time, gap, stable
                    FROM ohlc_candles
                    WHERE time > c1.time
                    ORDER BY time ASC
                    LIMIT 1
                ) c2 ON true
                WHERE c1.time >= $1
                AND c1.stable = true
                AND c2.time > c1.time + INTERVAL '1 minute'
                AND c2.stable = true
                AND c2.gap = false
                ORDER BY c1.time ASC
